This is the communication_simulation-write-a-block package meant as a guide to building
out-of-tree packages. To use the communication_simulation blocks, the Python namespaces
is in 'communication_simulation', which is imported as:

    import communication_simulation

See the Doxygen documentation for details about the blocks available
in this package. A quick listing of the details can be found in Python
after importing by using:

    help(communication_simulation)
